content: Is anyone here involved in the HIMSS Nordic Community Interoperability Project mentioned on https://www.himsseuropeconference.eu/helsinki/2019/nordic-workshop?
nope - is it for tech savy people or more sort of political people?
Hey - how we set for meeting in Stockholm Jun 7? Do we have a location and do we need to do any work on agenda?

Plan from our wednesday call:
- Sweden sends out an agenda proposal to the Nordic Cooperation group next week
- Agenda is set and communicated through each participant in the group
- The agenda is sent to Grahame so that he can prepare for the discussions

We have four proposed topics, but we're setting for two (maybe a third as backup, but time is limited)
Is the final invitation ready, so we can book the flight? @Oskar Thunman
Yes, we can confirm the event, and an updated invite and details on how to signup has been distributed to the participants of our monthly calls.
